OL,5, A senior officer has admitted racism   
OL,6, remains a problem in the Met Police,   
OL,7, after two black colleagues told the BBC
OL,8, that discrimination was getting worse. 
OL,10,FDeputy Assistant Commissioner Bas Javid
OL,11,Ftold BBC Newsnight some officers "have 
OL,12,Fracist views and are racist".          
OL,14,FBut he denied the Met was a "racist    
OL,15,Forganisation".                         
OL,17,FOne officer said a supervisor called   
OL,18,Fhim a racist slur, while another said  
OL,19,Fsenior leaders suggested black people  
OL,20,Fwere not clever enough for the Met.    
